features: [Powerful Suction with Upgraded Brushless Motor] The FABULETTA FSV003 cordless vacuum cleaner is equipped with a high-performance 29.6V Brushless Motor, delivering an impressive 25Kpa Strong Suction on MAX mode. Whether it's dust, dirt, or pet hair, this cordless vacuum cleaner ensures thorough cleaning on various surfaces, leaving your home spotless. Choose different suction modes(Max/Standard/Eco) according to different scenarios to reduce power consumption.

[Fast 4-Hour Charging and 50-Minute Runtime] The FABULETTA rechargeable Cordless Stick Vacuum Cleaner features a detachable 8x2500mAh large capacity battery, providing max 50 minutes of cleaning in Eco Mode. For continuous cleaning sessions, you can purchase an additional battery separately to double the runtime, ensuring a comprehensive and uninterrupted whole-house cleaning experience.

[6-in-1 Multi-function Vacuum for Versatile Cleaning] FABULETTA lightweight cordless stick Vacuum Cleaners for home come with a range of accessories, including a Power Floor Brush with LED light, Long crevice tool, Dust Brush, and adjustable Telescopic Alloy Tube. These components can be assembled into six configurations, making it easy to clean low pile carpets, floors, sofas, stairs, cars, and upholstered surfaces, bring you the best cleaning performance and efficiency!

[Flexible LED Motorized Brush Head] The floor brush head has a built-in independent motor for extra power. The LED headlights of the floor brush illuminate the dust, debris, and hair under furniture or other hard-to-reach dark corner and track it. flexible 150° sideways rotation and 90° up and down rotation let you clean the dust under furniture and bed. Relaxing your wrist and arm with an ergonomic handle. The lightweight main vacuum is only 3.3lbs, effortless to carry around, ensuring hassle-free cleaning in every room.

[High-Efficiency HEPA Filtration System for Cleaner Air] Our cordless stick vacuum cleaner features a 6-stage fully sealed cyclone filtration system, capturing 99.99% of dust particles as small as 0.1 microns. This advanced system ensures the release of ultimate purified air while effectively preventing secondary pollution, providing your family with fresher air.

[Warranty and After-Sales Service] Enjoy a worry-free purchase with FABULETTA's 12-month warranty service and 24-hour after-sales support. Our dedicated customer service team is available via email or phone to assist you with any questions or concerns regarding the FABULETTA Cordless Vacuum Cleaner. Please have your order number and product model ready when contacting customer support for a premium purchasing experience.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It’s not a Dyson but ok
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. You get what you pay for. Works best fully charged. Not bad for the money. Easy for my 10 year old to use and that was the reason that I purchased it for. Not that heavy. Suction slows down a little as it starts to fill up or battery is about to die. Battery last long enough to vacuum more than a room and steps by a child lol.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars I love it!
reviews.reviewText: I just got it. So far I love it!! Super easy to use and glides across my hard tile floors well!! The suction power works well! The battery works for my house. Only have 1 bed 1 bath house. By the time I'm done with the floors, couches, blinds, and hard to reach areas it's running on low; but not low enough to lose suction!! Definitely excited to see how it holds up over time!!! 🤞

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars LOVE, LOVE, LOVE IT
reviews.reviewText: I consider my home to be clean but this sucker be finding dirt everywhere lol. So now I am obsessed and vacuum daily. It’s easy to use and light weight. Even my 3 year old uses it. Powerful and at a great price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Great for those quick cleaning needs like lint off the dryer, or dust bunnies. It’s good on carpet too but I don’t think it’s powerful enough to be your only vacuum to deep clean carpets.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Limpio casas y está aspiradora hace su trabajo, entra en todas las áreas y es muy liviana. Solo dura 90 minutos la carga, así q solo te durará para una casa, si tienes compañía grande de limpieza está no es para ti. Me gusta porq la uso para aspirar mi carro también y que la ajustas de manera corta para diferentes trabajos, como percianas, sillones rincones etc

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Horrible- do not waste your money
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this because I had the older model, which I loved, but it only lasted a year- mind you, I use it only in hard floors, we have no carpet. This one is garbage. The suction won’t even pick up cat litter without 3-4 passes, dog hair clogs it and the handle will not stay extended and collapses with just the weight of the motor. It’s already in the garbage- I can’t even be bothered returning it. Stay away

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars So far so good!
reviews.reviewText: I love how it sucks up right up to the edges and sides of walls, furniture etc. very good suction and gets the dog hairs off my hard floors. My only issue is that it's almost as if the inside of the hose is coated in something sticky because everything seems to cling and build in the hose and clogs from time to time, it's a pain the clear the hose but other than that I'm very pleased with it's performance and the battery life is AMAZING!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars works well don't hesitate .
reviews.reviewText: let me just start off saying I was very skeptical and I'm sure everyone says that but for the price don't hesitate. you'll wish you didn't .so I had back surgery and can't bend down well yet so I needed something that wasn't heave and could reach and it works perfect . come with all the attachments u will need and so far so good I've used it about 10tl times so far and no complaints . the one thing tho is that you get about 20-30 charge if you use it on high speed witch ant to bad. take the chance if you don't like it return it simple . 2thumbs up 👍🏻👍🏻
I love how light and easy it is to use. It doesn’t have an Australian plug so I got an adapter and it works great. The best thing is you can buy extra battery packs.
